<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>DT-466E and 530E Diesel Engine Service (1995 through 1999) - SECTION 12: HIGH PRESSURE LUBE OIL SYSTEM -
        HIGH PRESSURE PUMP - INSTALLATION
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="3">
        <title>INSTALLATION</title>
        <para>Use the following steps to install the high pressure lube oil pump.</para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">
                <emph type="bold">On Engines With S/N 988150 &#38; Below:</emph>Place new gasket onto high pressure pump
                and place the pigh pressure pump into its location.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">
                <emph type="bold">On Engines With S/N 988151 &#38; Up:</emph>Install a new face seal into the groove of
                the front cover and place the pigh pressure pump into its location.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install two (2) capscrews and secure the high pressure pump to the front cover. Tighten the
                mounting bolts to the special torque value (
                <emph type="bold">Figures
                    <hotlnk xrefid="f1601229">12.29</hotlnk>
                </emph>
                ).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">If removed, install IPR valve into the high pressure pump. Tighten valve to the special
                torque value (
                <emph type="bold">Figure
                    <hotlnk xrefid="f1601230">12.30</hotlnk>
                </emph>
                ).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the IPR valve sleeve and solenoid to the IPR valve (
                <emph type="bold">Figure
                    <hotlnk xrefid="f1601231">12.31</hotlnk>
                </emph>
                ).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1601229" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="eg6874" filename="../figeg6/EG6874.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 12.29 Remove High Pressure Oil Pump On Engines S/N 988151 &#38; Up</caption>
            </figure>
            <figure id="f1601230" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="eg5105" filename="../figeg5/EG5105.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 12.30 Install IPR Valve</caption>
            </figure>
            <figure id="f1601231" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="eg5103" filename="../figeg5/EG5103.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 12.31 Install IPR Sleeve &#38; Solenoid</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">1. IPR Valve</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">2. Solenoid</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">3. Sleeve</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install and tighten tinnermann nut to the special torque value (
                <emph type="bold">Figure
                    <hotlnk document="e160_285.xml" xrefid="f1601232">12.32</hotlnk>
                </emph>
                ).
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
